(116, 1, '2018-04-02 14:39:35', '2018-04-02 14:39:35', '<h2>Incomplete Koitekok</h2>\r\nKoitekok is incomplete and in need of several improvements and additions in order to make it "whole".\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>For starters, Koitekok is still lacking in tenses and aspects, although they will be published into Ideas, and then added soon after.</li>\r\n 	<li>Koitekok still need a method for making new vocabulary (on my end) and a basic foundation of vocabulary that will allow it to be spoken without hitches or a need to make new vocab mid-sentence.</li>\r\n 	<li>Finally, this website is in need of a renewal of a code snippet (larger?) that will make tooltips on Koitekok spans which will display an IPA transcription of the selected Koitekok text.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThat concludes my first entry into KarlsLanguageHub.[(???) please alter this to reflect the web domain''s actual address],\r\nI hope this website will be able to flourish with my ideas so long as I make them.', 'Entry #1: Incomplete Sections and Improvements to Current Grammar', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'entry-1-incomplete-sections-and-improvements-to-current-grammar', '', '', '2018-04-02 14:39:35', '2018-04-02 14:39:35', '', 0, 'https://koitekok-blog-thepogobro.c9users.io/?p=116', 0, 'post', '', 0),
